history.pushState()
history.replaceState() 

The following are some of the main sinks can lead to DOM-based denial-of-service vulnerabilities:
requestFileSystem()
RegExp() 

 The following are some of the main sinks that can lead to DOM-XSS vulnerabilities:

document.write()
